5 guys. 5 stars. I've eaten burgers all over the US, Europe, and Asia. There are some better burgers out there, but not as a chain restaurant, and not for just 9 bucks. Their burgers are juicy and delicious. Their fries are so fresh that they taste like they cut the potatoes that day and fry them up. The texture varies but you can find both soft and crispy fries in each batch. The milkshakes are great. They have the usual flavors, MALT (it tastes like the Whopper candy), and have oreo cookies and oreo filling as two separate flavors for those that only want one of the two in their shake. Oh yes, and the customer service is great in general but also at this specific restaurant.
